The current code assumes that `SpendBlock` can only fail when `state.IsInvalid()` is true.
However, in the `BLOCK_MUTATED` path, `SpendBlock` calls `FatalError()`, which sets the state to `IsError()` instead of `IsInvalid()`.
As a result, this assertion can cause the node to crash.

```diff
